trans-unit.source: Represents a control that displays an image.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en kontroll som viser et bilde.

trans-unit.source: The Image class enables you to load the following image types: .bmp, .gif, .ico, .jpg, .png, .wdp, and .tiff.
trans-unit.target: Klassen bildet gjør det mulig å laste inn følgende bildetyper: BMP, GIF, *.ico, JPG, PNG, .wdp og TIFF.

trans-unit.source: When displaying a multiframe image, only the first frame is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Når du viser et multiframe bilde, vises bare den første rammen.

trans-unit.source: The animation of multiframe images is not supported by the Image control.
trans-unit.target: Animasjonen av multiframe bilder støttes ikke av bildet.

trans-unit.source: Until the image content is loaded, the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A> of the control will report as zero, because the image content is used to determine the final size and location of the control.
trans-unit.target: Før image-innholdet er lastet inn, den <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A>i kontrollen skal rapporten som null, image-innhold brukes til å fastslå endelig størrelsen og plasseringen av kontrollen.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualHeight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.ActualWidth%2A>

trans-unit.source: For a fixed size control, the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A> and/or <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A> properties can be set.
trans-unit.target: For en fast Størrelseskontroll av <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A>og/eller <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A>Egenskaper kan angis.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, to preserve the media's aspect ratio, set the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A> properties but not both.
trans-unit.target: Men hvis du vil beholde det mediet størrelsesforhold, angitt i <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A>Egenskaper, men ikke begge deler.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Height%2A> </xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Width%2A>

trans-unit.source: A value of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch> will cause your image to stretch to completely fill the output area.
trans-unit.target: Verdien <xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch>vil føre til at bildet skal strekkes for å fylle hele utskrift.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch>

trans-unit.source: When the output area and the image have different aspect ratios, the image is distorted by this stretching.
trans-unit.target: Når utskrift og bildet har forskjellige sideforhold, fordreid bildet av denne strekkes.

trans-unit.source: To make an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Image> preserve the aspect ratio of the image, set this property to <xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch> (default) or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch>.
trans-unit.target: Foreta en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Image>beholde størrelsesforholdet for bildet, angi denne egenskapen <xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch>(standard) eller <xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Stretch> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Image>
